description: Welcoming you in to your new Boston home this unit offers some conveniences including an off street parking space, in unit laundry, private extra storage, an open floor plan and many conveniences of the surrounding neighborhood. The condo's charm extends outdoors to an eclosed private patio; despite its below-ground locale, you'll find the surrounding area vibrant and inviting. Engage with nature and community spirit at the nearby Joe Moakley Park, perfect for morning jogs or leisurely evenings. Essential amenities are conveniently accessible, close proximity to Castle Island and beaches. Step through the door and be greeted by a spacious living area, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing after a long day. The primary bedroom promises serenity and privacy, complemented by an en-suite bathroom that enhances the suite's appeal. The additional bedroom can serve as a cozy guest room or your very own home. This open floor plan is warm and welcoming!
